# =============================================================================
# PrsmTechInc CODEOWNERS
# =============================================================================
# This file defines the code owners for the repository. Code owners are
# automatically requested for review when someone opens a pull request
# that modifies code they own.
#
# CODEOWNERS Structure:
#   - Each line is a file pattern followed by one or more owners
#   - The last matching pattern takes precedence
#   - Owners can be @username, @org/team, or email addresses
#
# Reference: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
# =============================================================================


